@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/users

### 1. GET 用户详情，预期 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/1001

### 2. PUT 修改用户，预期 200
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Alice"
}

### 3. DELETE 用户，预期 204 且响应体为空
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1001

### 4. POST 创建用户，预期 201 和 Location 响应头
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Alice"
}